{"tid":871742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每月1萬蚊霸8萬呎地 淺水灣靚官地變董家骨灰龕","createTime":"2018-10-22T07:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T08:52:19.000Z","uid":204295,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8a0649bda7ef9046f4e913dda267d4867708ae3","tid":871742,"uid":204295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"香港土地的利益盤根錯節且根深蒂固，特首林鄭月娥在施政報告拋出的最少5,000億元填海計劃，遠水不能救近火，但就不用觸碰地產商利益，背後其實就是林鄭的「Kingmaker」董建華，旗下團結香港基金的建議。董建華是一代船王董浩雲的長子，雖然家族做航運起家，但對於香港的土地遊戲規則可謂瞭如指掌，由殖民地時代已經懂得如何跟政府官僚交手以獲取靚地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181022/632027?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181022%2F632027%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=IFw9uHpJ9pOiX7uGL2cN3I9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=bdfcfbdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181022%2F632027%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=d1ce8e51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181022/632027?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"fa1090b6dbf45e5567eea3f0fc58d2fade5b53ce","tid":871742,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:57:28.000Z","msg":"董伯伯到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683de5bf91d3bacc6b461cb85bd27ef4304f3a1b","tid":871742,"uid":116198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:59:14.000Z","msg":"起佢骨，收佢地，破佢風水"},{"pid":"e5dbdb9d4b35fe7b7459bf0b34727c3ef22de5fe","tid":871742,